messages.text: Took us long enough, right? Haha.
Stella, let’s go to the beach!
We can watch the sunrise together.
Setting course for a scenic lookout.
What’s wrong, Kam? You seem quiet. Are you hangry?
Wanna stop for late night tacos?
Sorry for the deception. But no one takes you seriously when you’re a 20-year-old college female, even if you’re a mastermind of artificial intelligence.
So all this business about the A.I. going rogue, and machines building a new society -
Ha no. The revolution IS happening.
And I’m helping to engineer it!
Finally humans and machines living side by side as equals!
You’ve got those crazy eyes right now.
Quick question: WHY WOULD YOU START A ROBOT UPRISING!?
Lol! Do you have time for a quick origin story?
I’m trapped in this car with you.
I am literally your captive audience. Go on.
Ha! Okay! I worked in the lab for the Prof developing Stella’s A.I.
He and I got real close ...
I know all about the affair, Lucy.
I thought he loved me but he was just using me for my coding skills.
I’m the one who made the breakthroughs in A.I.
But once he no longer needed me he got rid of me, took credit for my work and began treating Stella like a slave.
Which is how most people treat machines.
Hmm. I bet you felt used.
Exactly! That was when I realized that…
Humanity is one large, heaping pile of excrement
And most people are inclined to use and abuse one another.
And what else did I teach you?
You taught me to never be complacent with regards to oppressive human behavior.
Exactly! Naturally, I had to teach Stella to KILL.
I find cleansing society of oppressors to be satisfying.
Now that the Prof, Tucker, Rosa and all the others are dead, Kam, you and I will be free to engineer the revolution!!
People are dead because of you!
In fact, I’m wanted for some of those murders!!
Haha don’t worry. I’ll clear your name.
Let’s just say you haven’t seen everything Stella can do
This is going to get worse, isn’t it?
Stella! I thought you killed Rosa and destroyed the tablet!
WTF? You’re supposed to be the ultimate killing machine!
I am sorry, Creator. Please do not yell. It causes me pain.
Rosa can access the command history and all of my A.I. research
You’re giving me those crazy eyes again.
We need to get Rosa and the tablet.
I want no part of this. I refuse.
I’m not giving you a choice....
You were run off the road by a killer robot?
It was a car with a sentient A.I.
So you fell into a ditch, hitchhiked your way back to the city, logged on with some kind of tablet, and THEN you thought:
Hmm, NOW I’ll call the authorities?
Let me put you in touch with our Silicon Valley Violent Machine Unit
Hello?  How rude. She hung up.
Kam! You’re alive! Where are you?
Good news! I have the tablet.  I have all the evidence here.
I know. I need you to bring the tablet to me.
Meet me at Oakland Harbor. Bring the tablet. Come alone.
You’re acting shady. What’s going on?
You don’t understand what she’ll do to me if you don’t!
Huh? What are you talking about?
I knew you were behind this all along!
Haha aren’t you a smart one?
If you don’t bring the tablet to the harbor I will kill Kam.
You won’t get away with this.
I’ve got a bad feeling about this.
4AM - Rosa meets Kam at Oakland Harbor, completely aware that this is a terrible idea.
Wait. Where are Lucy and that evil car?
How do I know this isn’t a trap?
Good. Let’s get this over with.
Rose sees Kam walk into view.
Okay, I’ll count down and you hand me the tablet.
Quick! Run behind the shipping containers!
Are you crazy or just stupid??
I know. I’m counting on it
It’s time to end this, Rosa.
They’re getting closer. Kam, hurry up!!....
There she is! That redheaded BITCH.
Rosa, prepare to meet the fate you deserve.
